# Mailchimp (consultation form → add contact to audience)
# Get your API key: Account → Extras → API keys
# Get Audience ID: Audience → Audience dashboard → Settings → Audience name and defaults → Audience ID
# Create a merge field "Message" with tag MMERGE3 in Audience → Settings → Merge tags (optional)
MAILCHIMP_API_KEY=your-api-key-us2
MAILCHIMP_AUDIENCE_ID=your-audience-id

# Optional: merge tag for the "How can we help?" message (default: MMERGE3)
# MAILCHIMP_MERGE_TAG_MESSAGE=MMERGE3
